## 📱 Mobile Control

### Bluetooth Commands

| Command | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `FWD` | Move forward |
| `BWD` | Move backward |
| `LEFT` | Turn left |
| `RIGHT` | Turn right |
| `STOP` | Stop motors |
| `GOTO:LAT,LON` | Navigate to GPS coordinates |
| `POS` | Get current position |
| `CLEAR` | Cancel navigation |

### Recommended Apps
- **Android:** Serial Bluetooth Terminal (free)
- **iOS:** BLE Terminal (requires HM-10 module instead of HC-05)

