## 🛠️ Hardware Specifications

### Core Components
- **Controller:** Arduino Mega 2560
- **Motors:** 4x TT DC Motors (3-6V)
- **Motor Drivers:** 2x L298N H-Bridge
- **GPS:** NEO-6M Module (±2.5m accuracy)
- **Bluetooth:** HC-05 Classic Bluetooth (~10m range)
- **Battery:** 7.4V 2200mAh Li-Po (2S)
- **Power:** 2x LM2596 Buck Converters (7.4V → 5V)

### Performance
- **Speed:** ~0.5 m/s (1.8 km/h)
- **Runtime:** 1.5 hours continuous, 3 hours typical delivery pattern
- **Waypoint Accuracy:** ±3 meters
- **GPS Update Rate:** 1 Hz
- **Weight Capacity:** ~1-2 kg (depends on chassis)

