## 🔧 Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Motors don't spin | Check L298N power, verify pin connections |
| GPS no fix | Move outdoors, wait 60s, check antenna up |
| Bluetooth won't pair | Check HC-05 power, voltage divider installed |
| Robot drives in circles | Calibrate motor speeds in code |
| Waypoint not reached | Increase WAYPOINT_THRESHOLD to 5m |

See [SETUP_GUIDE.md](SETUP_GUIDE.md) Part 5 for detailed troubleshooting.

