## 🔒 Safety Guidelines

- ⚠️ Test in controlled environments first
- ⚠️ Keep robot in visual line of sight
- ⚠️ Have emergency STOP ready
- ⚠️ Don't operate near traffic or crowds
- ⚠️ Li-Po battery safety: never over-discharge, use fireproof bag when charging
- ⚠️ Voltage divider required for HC-05 RX (3.3V logic)

